WEBVTT

00:02:57.244 --> 00:03:00.641
and coming from a country where
there are far more sheep than people,

00:03:00.665 --> 00:03:02.490
she'd always wanted to travel.

00:03:02.514 --> 00:03:05.717
She'd just landed her dream job
in marketing for Virgin Atlantic.

00:03:06.146 --> 00:03:08.305
She jumped at the chance
to work for her idol.

00:03:08.329 --> 00:03:09.996
SRO: When I was in college,

00:03:10.020 --> 00:03:14.953
Richard Branson and the original
Virgin Airlines had really ascended,

00:03:14.977 --> 00:03:21.875
and he just represented such an incredibly
awesome antiestablishment view

00:03:21.899 --> 00:03:24.262
that I just personally
really connected with.

00:03:24.798 --> 00:03:28.824
AG: And it didn't take long
before Sarah was making waves at Virgin.

00:03:28.848 --> 00:03:31.935
She pitched an ad campaign
to Sir Richard himself.